- keepIndex: If duplicate, which one to keep (0-based index, usually the last/latest); if not duplicate, fill -1
- reason: Brief reason for the judgment (within 20 characters)

Example output:
{"isDuplicate": true, "keepIndex": 1, "reason": "Both feedbacks describe the same connection issue"}
{"isDuplicate": false, "keepIndex": -1, "reason": "Feedbacks describe different feature issues"}

